metadata.editComments: Fixed some chords. It's necessary to learn to use omitted chords (omit3, omit5), not just use natural chords because they sound very loud, more than vocals. And in the post-chorus there's a slight inversion between F minor and Ab Major, they're not entirely Fm, but you're right in the intro they're natural E major chords and not with a G#m inversion. Btw thanks for fixing the notes, some chords and especially for adding the missing notes in the other songs of 'GUTS' by Olivia <3. You missed checking 'all-american girl'.
